OL,3,CIslanders urged to watch out for Asian
OL,4,Chornets after first nest spotted
OL,6,FIslanders in Guernsey are being urged
OL,7,Fto 'watch out' for Asian hornet queens
OL,8,Fon the island, after the first nest of
OL,9,Fthe year has been spotted early.
OL,11,FResidents identified a nest in a tree
OL,12,Fnext to St Saviour's Reservoir - which
OL,13,Fmay have already successfully housed
OL,14,Fnew queens.
OL,16,FAsian hornets pose a risk to
OL,17,Fresidents, as they are very
OL,18,Faggressive, and their stings can cause
OL,19,Fanaphylactic shock.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/7
