OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1773176765
OL,3,CIslanders urged to watch out for Asian
OL,4,Chornets after first nest spotted
OL,6,FThis is where the body has a severe
OL,7,Fallergic reaction, often leading to
OL,8,Fhospitalisation, and in extreme cases
OL,9,Finvolving multiple stings, death.
OL,11,FIn most cases however, Asian hornets'
OL,12,Fstings will only feel slightly more
OL,13,Fpainful than those from a wasp.
OL,15,FIn addition to their threat to humans,
OL,16,Fthe RSPB have warned that they are a
OL,17,F'significant predator' to honey bees.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
