CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1773176765
OL,3,CIslanders urged to watch out for Asian
OL,4,Chornets after first nest spotted
OL,6,FAs temperatures begin to rise, Asian
OL,7,Fhornet queens are expected to emerge
OL,8,Ffrom their winter hibernation, and
OL,9,Fwill begin seeking sources of food and
OL,10,Fspots to nest.
OL,12,FGuernsey's government have warned that
OL,13,Fthese queens are most likely to visit
OL,14,Fflowering camellias in gardens, or
OL,15,Fbuild nests in bird boxes or
OL,16,Foutbuildings.
OL,18,FEach nest can hold as many as 2,000
OL,19,Fhornets.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
