PN,38304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1773176765
OL,3,CIslanders urged to watch out for Asian
OL,4,Chornets after first nest spotted
OL,6,FAsian hornets are recognisable through
OL,7,Fthe orange stripes on their bodies,
OL,8,Fwhich are much darker than the yellow
OL,9,Flace which is typical of their
OL,10,FEuropean counterparts.
OL,12,FThey are also much smaller than
OL,13,FEuropean hornets.
OL,15,FAsian Hornets are generally between 20-
OL,16,F24mm, barely larger than a common
OL,17,Fwasp, whereas European hornets can
OL,18,Freach sizes of up to 35mm.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
