OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1773176765
OL,3,CIslanders urged to watch out for Asian
OL,4,Chornets after first nest spotted
OL,6,FTo combat the rise of Asian hornets,
OL,7,FGuernsey's government is launching its
OL,8,Fannual Spring Queening campaign.
OL,10,FThis involves 230 volunteers who track
OL,11,Fand catch queen hornets before they
OL,12,Fcan start a nest.
OL,14,FIf Islanders on the Bailiwick spot
OL,15,FAsian hornets, they are being urged to
OL,16,Falert the authorities by emailing
OL,17,Fasianhornet@gov.gg or by telephoning
OL,18,Feither 01481 220110 or 07839197082.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
