OL,3,CIslanders urged to watch out for Asian
OL,4,Chornets after first nest spotted
OL,6,FJersey residents can also expect to
OL,7,Fsee Asian hornets in the coming
OL,8,Fmonths, after their numbers on the
OL,9,Fisland increased tenfold between 2021
OL,10,Fand 2025.
OL,12,FIf spotted in Jersey, residents should
OL,13,Freport Asian Hornet sightings to
OL,14,Fasianhornet@gov.je or call +44
OL,15,F1534441633.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
